data.title: New York City, United States
data.meta_description: The Rockefeller Foundation exercises unwavering commitments to urban experimentation, civic responsibility, and creative expression in our hometown.
data.text: New York’s streetscapes serve as more than a setting for our work. This city, which faces its own unique list of challenges, inspires and informs an active appreciation for and investment in the strength, resilience, and cultural innovation of cities around the world. The Rockefeller Foundation exercises unwavering commitments to urban experimentation, civic responsibility, and creative expression in our hometown—practices that expand into our global initiatives as well.
